OL,3,CCharity shop spends thousands on CCTV
OL,4,Cafter spate of shoplifting
OL,6,FA charity shop said it has spent
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds on CCTV in an
OL,8,Feffort to stop thieves from
OL,9,Fshoplifting.
OL,11,FThe charity Making a Difference to
OL,12,FMaidstone helps people in crisis
OL,13,Fdealing with poverty, homelessness,
OL,14,Faddiction and social isolation.
OL,16,FStaff at the Kent charity say their
OL,17,Fwork is being hindered every day by
OL,18,Fshoplifting.
