OL,3,CCharity shop spends thousands on CCTV
OL,4,Cafter spate of shoplifting
OL,6,FThefts have not stopped despite the
OL,7,Fteam monitoring cameras, moving the
OL,8,Fchanging room to opposite the till and
OL,9,Finstalling mirrors.
OL,11,FEmma Colhoun, staff at Making a
OL,12,FDifference to Maidstone said: "We have
OL,13,Fthe fantastic range, but we also try
OL,14,Fto keep all of our prices quite low.
OL,16,F"So, when people are stealing from us,
OL,17,Fthey're stealing objects and items of
OL,18,Fclothing that usually are under sort
OL,19,Fof six, seven pounds.
