OL,3,CCharity shop spends thousands on CCTV
OL,4,Cafter spate of shoplifting
OL,6,F"It's quite heartbreaking because
OL,7,Fpeople aren't taking essentials.
OL,9,F"The things that are being stolen, are
OL,10,Fhigh price items. So I'm not convinced
OL,11,Fthat all of the thefts that we have
OL,12,Fare from people that need it.
OL,14,F"I believe a lot of it is being taken
OL,15,Fby people that just want it."
OL,17,FRob Foley, Charity Manager: "The less
OL,18,Fthefts we have, the more we sell and
OL,19,Fthe more we can help.
