OL,3,CCharity shop spends thousands on CCTV
OL,4,Cafter spate of shoplifting
OL,6,F"That's, that's the point of a
OL,7,Fcharity. That's our charitable purpose
OL,8,Fto help people. But it's all the work
OL,9,Fand admin around the theft that really
OL,10,Ftakes the time."
OL,12,FKent Police said recent shoplifting
OL,13,Ffigures are improving in West Kent but
OL,14,Fnot in Maidstone.
OL,16,FInsp Steve Kent, Kent Police said:
OL,17,F"It's a problem in Maidstone. As I
OL,18,Fsaid, I think it's a problem
OL,19,Fnationally. We are doing our utmost
OL,20,Fto, to reduce that problem.
