OL,6,F"I'm confident in the work that we are
OL,7,Fdoing. It's not just police led, it is
OL,8,Fmulti-layered.
OL,10,F"We are working, with our partners,
OL,11,Fwith the stakeholders, with the
OL,12,Fbusinesses, with the individual
OL,13,Fmembers of staff to gather the
OL,14,Fintelligence, to look, to prosecute
OL,15,Fthese people."
